public class AVLTree<E extends java.lang.Comparable>
extends BinarySearchTree<E>

An implementation of AVL tree which inherits from a binary search tree Algorithms are based on Evangel Quiwa's pseudocode on AVLTrees

Author:
Anter Aaron Custodio & Carl Zachery Viernes CS123 - UP Manila
